My 3rd map course based on a theme dev textures. She has 14 traps & 1 bonus.
The map contains :

Songs :

*Avicii - Levels (Radiot Edit)

*Swedish House Mafia - Greyhound (Radio Edit) - Unofficial

Secrets :

*1 Secret (Bonus)

*1 Bonus (Climb)

*4 Smoke + 1 Grenade

Fixed bugs 29/08/2013 :

*Water bug in the bunny hop.

*Damage in the end.

Map created for my team Destiny Clan.
Visit destiny-clan.fr & Steam group http://steamcommunity.com/groups/teamdestiny-clan. 
Map project by HARDCORE.

Enjoy !
